data.add-delite-to-your-hardhat-config#Add De:
For the accounts array, you will need to enter the private key of the account you are deploying the contract with. It is not recommended to hardcode the private key like this (an environment variable would be better, but is still risky).Use a throwaway wallet to be safe. Don't reveal the private key of a wallet with significant value!

